platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: With Free App of the Week, we highlight a great app you can enjoy at no charge this week. (In-App Purchases sold separately.) ZeptoLabs highly anticipated sequel is an absolute blast, filled with endless charm and brilliantly designed physics-based puzzles. Use all-new allies and abilities to feed the adorable Om Nom candy while navigating each stages unique layout and collecting stars along the way. With new mechanics smartly layered onto the series already famous gameplay, Cut the Rope 2 is continually challenging and engaging.
